data.description: Lovely ranch style home with sparking swimming in a popular well-established neighborhood.  New flooring in kitchen, tile backsplash, breakfast bar and pantry.  All 3 bedrooms have new vinyl floors, Primary has full bath with tub / jack & jill. The living room and dining room have refinished original hardwoods, hall bath remodeled, new paint throughout entire home. Char railing & crown molding.  Nice sunny den with brick fireplace, gorgeous wormwood walls. Kitchen has tile backsplash, new floors, breakfast bar, pantry. The large front room could be a formal living room or dining room. Huge deck with gazebo and pool with new pump & upgraded filtration. Heated and cooled space in basement, also tons of space for storage, laundry room. Extra driveway around back to garage, lots of garden space, mature trees and flowering bushes/magnolias. Lovely corner lot, great location, close to shopping and restaurants. New roof!  See agent only.
